public abstract class ModelCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<Model>, java.io.Serializable

An common interface for substitution models, that includes some specific operations to work with model collections.

addModelCartesian

public boolean addModelCartesian(java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> matrices,

                                 java.util.Properties modelProperties,
                                 pal.alignment.Alignment alignment,
                                 pal.tree.Tree tree,
                                 int ncat)
Adds the models result of combine each matrix with each distribution. There will be MxD new models in the iterator, where M is the number of matrices D is the number of distributions

Parameters:
matrices - collection of all the substitution matrices
distributions - collection of all the distributions
modelProperties - the model properties
Returns:
true, if successfully added all models
